  "body": "### Description\n\nWe want to be able to pull the latest image when we run our test in-order to keep the test environment up to date.\r\n\r\nIt would be nice if we could set the pull policy in the configuration like e.g.\r\n\r\n`quarkus.datasource.devservices.pull-policy=allways`\r\n\r\nPrimarily we need this for the database, but it may be useful for all devsevices.\r\n\r\nIf I did not manually clean my images, then we could end up with an outdated image after some time.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nThe devservice code seems to need some housekeeping as well. It may be a good idea to use a common devservice base and share properties along the way.",
